%N A015659 Inverse of 1650th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015659 Periodic with period length 1650. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015659 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015659/b015659.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015659 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1650.
%H A015659 <a href="/index/Rec#order_400">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 400.
%H A015659 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015659 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
